    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> to a bowl with most of your <strong>cornflour</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and mix until evenly coated</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated meat-free chick'n</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until golden and crispy all over, reserve the bowl – this is your <strong>crispy meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
