      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into small pieces</p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into small pieces</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
